A vintage 1970s computer terminal setup with warm amber and sepia tones, showing a wooden desk with an old CRT monitor displaying cascading streams of curly braces and colons representing JSON data. Beside it, a worn leather-bound dictionary lies open, its pages transforming into flowing ribbons of code that spiral upward. The scene is bathed in soft tungsten lighting from a brass desk lamp, with scattered punch cards and coffee-stained technical manuals creating an atmosphere of methodical problem-solving. The color palette emphasizes browns, oranges, and cream, with the monitor's amber glow as the focal point.
